targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  InternalPumpLeakage
FROM metrics
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  CoolerCondition, ValveCondition, InternalPumpLeakage, HydraulicAccumulator, StableFlag
FROM metrics_predict15
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  ValveCondition
FROM metrics
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  HydraulicAccumulator
FROM metrics
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  StableFlag
FROM metrics
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  CoolerCondition
FROM metrics
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter("timestamp")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  time AS "time",
  value
FROM rawdata
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(time)
ORDER BY 1
